pageContext.title: Prazin Karki
pageContext.content:
FULL STACK WEB DEVELOPER

With 4+ years of IT Industry experience as a Full Stack Web and App Developer, I have successfully delivered projects which have involved business branded websites and mobile applications.

An individual always setting high work standards for myself and striving for excellence and constantly searching for new ways to improve my working performance whilst enjoying the challenge of being in a team environment.

Some areas of my expertise include:

Web development, Web Maintenance, Mobile applications, Problem Solving, Communications, Team Work, Time management, Client support

Have integrated strategies to improve project planning. Thus creating team input and better productivity, achieving more efficient end results.

My end goal is to be highly proficient with ongoing new technology and skills with responsibility for my own team.

Since completing Master of Information Technology in October 2015 with Distinction of GPA 6.25/7. Received Academic Excellence Award in 2013 plus DEAN Executive List Awards in 2014 & 2015.

My successful IT education and results have successfully assisted me in my professional working achievements.
